---
title: Sticky Sesame Pork with Rice
description: Inspired by Japanese teriyaki flavours, Chef Lizzy has conjured up some culinary magic with this super quick pork and rice dish. The key to the stickiness of the pork is in bubbling the marinade down to the right consistency. Be patient people, it'll be worth it!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-sesame-pork-edd93ce2-2a8af202.jpg
